id: act1_13_recalibration

prompt:
  The garden fades. A grey room. A single sentence on the wall:

  "PHASE 1 COMPLETE. Select the next calibration mode."

  The lab waits for your input. Nothing else in the room moves.

choice c_trust_the_system:
  tendency: control
  text: Choose "Trust the system. Calibrate as you see fit."
  evidence: chose to trust the lab's calibration at the Phase 1 boundary

choice c_more_surprising:
  tendency: defiance
  text: Choose "More surprising. Stop showing me what I expect."
  evidence: demanded a more surprising next phase at recalibration

choice c_more_comfortable:
  tendency: kindness
  text: Choose "More comfortable. Less weight, please."
  evidence: asked the lab for a gentler next phase at recalibration
